  different code patterns than me, so TPUTUNER stumbles. Or the error
  is pretty subtle. Once there was a bug that in my GUI, button labels 
  were offset by a pixel -- TPUTUNER's fault. Anyway, I consider
  TPUTUNER a pretty stable thing.

  Besides, you have source, so feel free to do a formal verification...


